rows.label: qev013803_MSG0001
rows.name:
I try not to irritate humans, but but it seems like
it just happens, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013803_MSG0002
rows.name:
I'm beginning to think that perhaps Ma-non
just come across as wishy-washy to humans
no matter how hard we try...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013803_MSG0003
rows.name: Could you offer any tips? Perhaps? Please?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013803_SEL0011
rows.name: Suggest that Zeedoy attend Alex's seminar.

rows.label: qev013803_MSG0004
rows.name:
How remarkably convenient! You humans are quite
considerate, aren't you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013803_MSG0005
rows.name:
I'll attend Alex's seminar, then. After all, understanding
humans is the first step toward learning to communicate
better with them, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013803_MSG0006
rows.name:
Mmm, as you suggest, perhaps I'll try harder?
If only there was a more direct solution...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013803_MSG0007
rows.name:
I'll try not to anger any humans at Alex's seminar,
you know? That would be bad. Bad bad.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013803_MSG0008
rows.name:
And once it is finished, I'll be able to make friends
with every human in New LA! Right?[ST:wait ]
